    "description": "Brought back to the world of the living, you'll need to <strong>survive</strong> as you <strong>explore</strong> stunningly beautiful worlds filled with danger.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749400/extras/1d6bd5064ac274f17e503cf3dc6e45ee.avif?t=1767816314\" width=622 height=119 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is Lendas?</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749400/extras/f720e1d4116dd759c42570c58eba34c1.webp?t=1767816314\" width=114 height=34 /></span>is a <strong>Survival</strong> and <strong>Exploration</strong> game with <strong>Action RPG</strong> elements. It takes place in <strong>procedurally generated worlds</strong> with <strong>living ecosystems</strong>. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749400/extras/b0a1de1573f7a3c2e8e7b4d3c681755c.poster.avif?t=1767816314\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749400/extras/b0a1de1573f7a3c2e8e7b4d3c681755c.webm?t=1767816314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749400/extras/b0a1de1573f7a3c2e8e7b4d3c681755c.mp4?t=1767816314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Face creatures inspired by the <strong>Brazilian folklore</strong> and <strong>steal their powers</strong> to bring you one step closer to your revenge.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749400/extras/06d18fc4e5640af37f6a58629cb36deb.poster.avif?t=1767816314\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749400/extras/06d18fc4e5640af37f6a58629cb36deb.webm?t=1767816314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749400/extras/06d18fc4e5640af37f6a58629cb36deb.mp4?t=1767816314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You will need to <strong>harvest</strong> resources, <strong>build items</strong>, <strong>hunt</strong> powerful creatures and <strong>build shelters</strong> that will help you survive.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749400/extras/4866aa2890c34fcfa6a3cd44cc540451.poster.avif?t=1767816314\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749400/extras/4866aa2890c34fcfa6a3cd44cc540451.webm?t=1767816314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749400/extras/4866aa2890c34fcfa6a3cd44cc540451.mp4?t=1767816314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Lendas</strong> has an advanced survival system, which features gathering and crafting items, a day and night system, and a hunger and thirst system.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749400/extras/9bc69f3ca57ce83bcecc40939fcb7ef6.poster.avif?t=1767816314\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749400/extras/9bc69f3ca57ce83bcecc40939fcb7ef6.webm?t=1767816314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749400/extras/9bc69f3ca57ce83bcecc40939fcb7ef6.mp4?t=1767816314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The <strong>character creation</strong> system is quite detailed. Players can change from eye distance to upper lip size.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749400/extras/7e5899fb2c9705141cbda2802543021c.poster.avif?t=1767816314\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749400/extras/7e5899fb2c9705141cbda2802543021c.webm?t=1767816314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749400/extras/7e5899fb2c9705141cbda2802543021c.mp4?t=1767816314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
